flowchart LR

  P["Press · t = 0 ms<br/>haptic tap · UI flash · band appears"]:::orbiter
  D["Drag · continuous<br/>dotted preview · rising tension audio · rumble"]:::planet
  R["Release · t ≈ 1200 ms<br/>launch SFX · screen shake 0.05 u · particle poof · camera zoom"]:::atmosphere
  S["Spawn · t + 16 ms<br/>orbiter sprite appears · debut squash/stretch"]:::success
  K["Pickups · t + 500 ms onward<br/>per-mass tic SFX · tiny bursts · counter pulse on tens digit"]:::debris
  E["Orbit-end · variable<br/>success chime or atmosphere-burn fade"]:::neutral

  P --> D --> R --> S --> K --> E

